description:
This is a 202 minute workout called '50 Best Running Songs of All Time' from the channel Men's Health Mag.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Adrenaline Rush vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Adrenaline Rush vibe means Heart-racing, full-body intensity, unpredictable challenges. This is especially good for Those who crave challenge, variety, and adrenaline..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
